  "text": "Androgen dependent miniaturization of scalp hair follicles by DHT is implicated as the primary cause of alopecia [CITATION_1] . Controlled clinical trials demonstrated that use of finasteride resulted in decreased accumulation of DHT and improvements in both subjective and objective assessments of hair growth and density [CITATION_2] .",
